---
project : projectinfo
version : '0.6'
status  : beta

title    : ProjectInfo
subtitle : The Project Metadata Class
description : >
  ProjectInfo is a deluxe project metadata class. ProjectInfo is highly versitile
  for managing project metadata. It can be converted to a Gem::Specification
  in a single command (to_gemspec) for building out gems packages, as well as other
  package management control specifications (deb, rpm, pkgbuild, etc.). ProjectInfo
  is designed to be the best solution for complementing build tools --it is extensible
  and can automatically load from a YAML configuration file.

